          <ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Type "about:policies" in the browser address bar.

If "PopupBlocking" is not displayed under Policy Name or the Policy Value is not "Default" "true", this is a finding.
If "PopupBlocking" is not displayed under Policy Name or the Policy Value is not "Locked" "true", this is a finding.

"PopupBlocking" "Enabled" may be used to specify an allowlist of sites where pop-ups are desired, this is optional.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
        </STIG_DATA>
        <STIG_DATA>
          <VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Fix_Text</VULN_ATTRIBUTE>
          <ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Windows group policy:
