          <ATTRIBUTE_DATA>JavaScript can make changes to the browser's appearance. This activity can help disguise an attack taking place in a minimized background window. Configure the browser setting to prevent scripts on visited websites from moving and resizing browser windows.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
