          <ATTRIBUTE_DATA>JavaScript can raise and lower browser windows to cause improper input. Configure the browser setting to prevent scripts on visited websites from raising and lowering browser windows.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
        </STIG_DATA>
        <STIG_DATA>
