        <STIG_DATA>
          <VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Vuln_Discuss</VULN_ATTRIBUTE>
          <ATTRIBUTE_DATA>The use of separate file systems for different paths can protect the system from failures resulting from a file system becoming full or failing.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
