          <VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Rule_Title</VULN_ATTRIBUTE>
          <ATTRIBUTE_DATA>The graphical display manager must not be installed on RHEL 8 unless approved.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
        </STIG_DATA>
        <STIG_DATA>
          <VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Vuln_Discuss</VULN_ATTRIBUTE>
          <ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Internet services that are not required for system or application processes must not be active to decrease the attack surface of the system. Graphical display managers have a long history of security vulnerabilities and must not be used, unless approved and documented.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
