        <FINDING_DETAILS>#echo "***XYLOK ICS***"
mount | grep /var/tmp
echo "***XYLOK ICS***"
grep "/var/tmp" /etc/fstab

Checking if '/var/tmp' is mounted with 'nosuid' option:
❌ '/var/tmp' is not mounted on the system.


Checking that the 'nosuid' is configured for '/var/tmp':
❌ '/var/tmp' is not configured in '/etc/fstab'.


