grep -Er '^[[:space:]]*user.max_user_namespaces' /run/sysctl.d/*.conf /usr/local/lib/sysctl.d/*.conf /usr/lib/sysctl.d/*.conf /lib/sysctl.d/*.conf /etc/sysctl.conf /etc/sysctl.d/*.conf 2&gt;/dev/null

Checking the value of the 'user.max_user_namespaces' variable:
❌ user.max_user_namespaces = 31588

Checking config files to enable 'user.max_user_namespaces' variable:
