        <STIG_DATA>
          <VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Vuln_Discuss</VULN_ATTRIBUTE>
          <ATTRIBUTE_DATA>If local interactive users are not assigned a valid home directory, there is no place for the storage and control of files they should own.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
