</FINDING_DETAILS>
        <COMMENTS>The 'disk_full_action' setting is set to 'SUSPEND' in the '/etc/audit/auditd.conf' file, but should be set to 'HALT', 'SYSLOG', or 'SINGLE'.
disk_full_action = SUSPEND</COMMENTS>
