        <STIG_DATA>
          <VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Vuln_Discuss</VULN_ATTRIBUTE>
          <ATTRIBUTE_DATA>The "shosts.equiv" files are used to configure host-based authentication for the system via SSH. Host-based authentication is not sufficient for preventing unauthorized access to the system, as it does not require interactive identification and authentication of a connection request, or for the use of two-factor authentication.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
