          <ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Configure the audit system to set the audit rules to be immutable by adding the following line to "/etc/audit/rules.d/audit.rules"

-e 2

Note: Once set, the system must be rebooted for auditing to be changed.  It is recommended to add this option as the last step in securing the system.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
