Checking the value of the 'fs.protected_symlinks' variable:
✅ fs.protected_symlinks = 1

Checking config files to enable 'fs.protected_symlinks' variable:
✅ /usr/lib/sysctl.d/50-default.conf:fs.protected_symlinks = 1
