        <STATUS>NotAFinding</STATUS>
        <FINDING_DETAILS>#echo '***XYLOK ICS***'
stat -c "%a %n" /sbin/auditctl /sbin/aureport /sbin/ausearch /sbin/autrace /sbin/auditd /sbin/rsyslogd /sbin/augenrules

Checking the mode of each audit tool:
✅ 755 /sbin/auditctl
✅ 755 /sbin/aureport
✅ 755 /sbin/ausearch
