          <VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Rule_Title</VULN_ATTRIBUTE>
          <ATTRIBUTE_DATA>All RHEL 8 local disk partitions must implement cryptographic mechanisms to prevent unauthorized disclosure or modification of all information that requires at rest protection.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
