grep -Er '^[[:space:]]*net.ipv4.conf.all.accept_redirects' /run/sysctl.d/*.conf /usr/local/lib/sysctl.d/*.conf /usr/lib/sysctl.d/*.conf /lib/sysctl.d/*.conf /etc/sysctl.conf /etc/sysctl.d/*.conf 2&gt;/dev/null

Checking the value of the 'net.ipv4.conf.all.accept_redirects' variable:
✅ net.ipv4.conf.all.accept_redirects = 0

Checking config files to enable 'net.ipv4.conf.all.accept_redirects' variable:
